{
  "texts": [
    "By suspending empirical assumptions, it isolates the structural space within which behavioral models may subsequently be embedded.",
    "In this sense, the category serves as a conceptual arena rather than a predictive mechanism.",
    "Example C illustrates how such an arena can nevertheless function as a paradigm for application.",
    "Consider a case in which an event occurs within a political world represented by a p-site a.",
    "The categorical framework requires only that, following this event, some morphism with domain a be selected."
  ]
}